OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779429952
OL,3,CInvestigation into Andrew to include
OL,4,Cclaims of sexual misconduct
OL,6,FDetectives investigating Andrew
OL,7,FMountbatten-Windsor will consider
OL,8,Fallegations of sexual misconduct in
OL,9,Ftheir inquiry into potential
OL,10,Fmisconduct in public office.
OL,12,FThe legal definition of the offence
OL,13,Fcan include a wide range of conduct,
OL,14,Fincluding sharing confidential
OL,15,Ffinancial information, financial
OL,16,Fmisconduct, wilful neglect of duty,
OL,17,Fand sexual misconduct.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779429952
OL,3,CInvestigation into Andrew to include
OL,4,Cclaims of sexual misconduct
OL,6,FIt also covers corruption and improper
OL,7,Finterference, conflict of interest,
OL,8,Fperverting the course of justice,
OL,9,Fdishonesty or fraudulent conduct,
OL,10,Fmisconduct leading to personal gain.
OL,12,FDetectives at Thames Valley Police
OL,13,F(TVP) are understood to be concerned
OL,14,Fthat the public believes they are only
OL,15,Ffocused on accusations that the former
OL,16,Fprince shared information while a
OL,17,Ftrade envoy, when in fact the legal
OL,18,Fterms of the offence under
OL,19,Finvestigation are much broader.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779429952
OL,3,CInvestigation into Andrew to include
OL,4,Cclaims of sexual misconduct
OL,6,FAndrew served as the UK's special
OL,7,Frepresentative for international trade
OL,8,Fand investment from 2001 until 2011,
OL,9,Fwhen he stepped down amid controversy
OL,10,Fover his friendship with paedophile
OL,11,Ffinancier Jeffrey Epstein.
OL,13,FHe has denied any wrongdoing over his
OL,14,Flinks to the convicted sex offender.
OL,16,FTVP's major investigation is expected
OL,17,Fto be lengthy, and will face obstacles
OL,18,Fincluding trying to prove whether
OL,19,FAndrew held a public office at the
OL,20,Ftime of the allegations, something
OL,21,Fthat is not clearly legally defined.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779429952
OL,3,CInvestigation into Andrew to include
OL,4,Cclaims of sexual misconduct
OL,6,FHowever it is understood that if this
OL,7,Fwere found not to be the case, the
OL,8,Fforce would continue investigating any
OL,9,Fevidence of other, separate offences.
OL,11,FA team of experienced investigators is
OL,12,Fworking on the case and is in constant
OL,13,Fcontact with prosecutors for advice.
OL,15,FOfficers are currently assessing a
OL,16,Fclaim by a woman that she was sent by
OL,17,FEpstein to Royal Lodge for sex with
OL,18,FAndrew in 2010, before being given a
OL,19,Ftour of Buckingham Palace.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779429952
OL,3,CInvestigation into Andrew to include
OL,4,Cclaims of sexual misconduct
OL,6,FThey have contacted the woman's
OL,7,Flawyer, Brad Edwards, who initially
OL,8,Fspoke to the BBC about allegations
OL,9,Fsaid to have occurred when she was in
OL,10,Fher 20s.
OL,12,FThe force said: "We have engaged with
OL,13,Fthe woman's legal representative to
OL,14,Fconfirm that, should she wish to
OL,15,Freport this to police, it will be
OL,16,Ftaken seriously and handled with care,
OL,17,Fsensitivity and respect for her
OL,18,Fprivacy and her right for anonymity.
OL,26,@tD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779429952
OL,3,CInvestigation into Andrew to include
OL,4,Cclaims of sexual misconduct
OL,6,F"We recognise how difficult it can be
OL,7,Fto speak about experiences of this
OL,8,Fnature, and any contact with police
OL,9,Fwill be led by her wishes, when and if
OL,10,Fshe feels ready and able to do so."
OL,12,FAndrew was arrested on suspicion of
OL,13,Fmisconduct in public office on
OL,14,FFebruary 19 and interviewed under
OL,15,Fcaution before being released under
OL,16,Finvestigation.
OL,18,FSearches were also carried out at his
OL,19,Fformer homes in Windsor and Norfolk.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
