PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779429952
OL,3,CInvestigation into Andrew to include
OL,4,Cclaims of sexual misconduct
OL,6,FDetectives are understood to be
OL,7,Fworking through evidence recovered
OL,8,Fduring the operation.
OL,10,FThey have also made a formal request
OL,11,Fto the United States Department of
OL,12,FJustice for the original versions of
OL,13,Fthe Epstein files, but have not yet
OL,14,Freceived any information.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
