CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1779429952
OL,3,CInvestigation into Andrew to include
OL,4,Cclaims of sexual misconduct
OL,6,FThames Valley Police Assistant Chief
OL,7,FConstable Oliver Wright said: "Our
OL,8,Fmisconduct in public office
OL,9,Finvestigation is continuing.
OL,10,FMisconduct in public office is a crime
OL,11,Fthat can take different forms, making
OL,12,Fthis a complex investigation.
OL,14,F"Our team of very experienced
OL,15,Fdetectives are working meticulously
OL,16,Fthrough a significant amount of
OL,17,Finformation that has come in from the
OL,18,Fpublic and other sources.
OL,26,@oD@_OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
