OL,6,F"I understand the high level of
OL,7,Finterest in this work, but please be
OL,8,Fpatient as we continue to actively
OL,9,Fprogress our investigation. We will
OL,10,Fprovide further updates to the public
OL,11,Fand media when appropriate."
